For flexible PSCs, repeated cyclic-bending fatigue tests were performed to evaluate the mechanical endurance. As illustrated in the inset of Fig. 5b, the minimum bending radius (r) is 3 mm, which corresponds to a maximum stress (σ) of 371 MPa, calculated using the following relation37:1σ=Eh2r\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
